relevant_findings.general: Alert and in no apparent distress
relevant_findings.ent: Ears and nose without visible erythema, masses, or trauma; Oropharynx without visible lesion, erythema or exudate; Mucous membranes moist
relevant_findings.respiratory: Lungs clear to auscultation with good air movement bilaterally
relevant_findings.gastrointestinal: Abdomen soft, tender to palpation in RUQ and epigastric regions
relevant_findings.musculoskeletal: Neck supple, moves all extremities, strength grossly full and symmetric bilaterally in all limbs
relevant_findings.neurological: Alert, oriented to self and 'that place where sick people go', tangential narrator, frequent difficulty with word finding though speech fluent, ambulates to the bathroom with assistance
